OL,7,FA pensioner has been jailed after
OL,8,Fhistorical sex offences towards girls
OL,9,Fdating back to the 1970s.
OL,11,FPeter David Long, 66, pleaded guilty
OL,12,Fto six counts of sexual intercourse
OL,13,Fwith a girl under the age of 13 and 13
OL,14,Fcounts of indecent assault.
OL,16,FThe 19 offences were against four
OL,17,Fgirls who were aged between seven and
OL,18,F14 at the time they were assaulted.
