OL,9,Flicence and a lifetime restraining
OL,10,Forder for all the complainants.
OL,12,FDetective Constable Georgia Davis of
OL,13,FSouth Wales Police, said: "It's
OL,14,Fentirely down to these women willing
OL,15,Fto speak to us regarding Long's
OL,16,Fdespicable actions that he'll now face
OL,17,Fthe consequences.
